import Home_left from './home_left/Home_left'
import Home_right from './home_right/Home_right'
import React from 'react'

export default function Home() {

    return ( <
        div className = "row"
        style = {
            { paddingTop: '20px' } } >
        <
        Home_left > < /Home_left> { /* <RouterHome/> */ } <
        Home_right > < /Home_right>

        <
        /div>
    )


}
